:FCC ID applies to FS1E5, FS1E5W, FS2E5, and FS2E5W.
"490YY500B-1.6mm" is silkscreened on the main board in the FCC photos. :"YYNOONOB-1.0" is silkscreened on the wireless module.
Hardware specs from the FCC photos differ from what :is in the FCC manual (256MB RAM, 512MB Flash). HTTP administration port appears to be 8080.
